The app has no body-parsing middleware. If you add `POST`/`PUT` routes (very likely as the app grows), unvalidated JSON bodies could lead to injection or DoS attacks.

**Add immediately:**
```js
app.use(express.json({ limit: '10kb' })); // Limit body size to prevent DoS
app.use(express.urlencoded({ extended: false, limit: '10kb' }));
```

